title: Soul Sisters Gathering
desc: Soul Sisters coming together to share, laugh, cry, uplift, support and celebrate each other. Each event will have a different topic and theme to discuss, share and explore. This event is held at Yogasmoga's Brentwood Store. We'll have time to shop and explore after the event! Come ready with a Yoga Mat (or pillow), Journal and a Smile. Love & Awakening, Elyse www.elysefalzone.com
